main event: In October 1947, a 'saucer' was sighted in Dodgeville, Wisconsin, moving slowly from NW to S, then suddenly circled in a burst of speed and moved towards the south, exhibiting no sound, smell, or trail.
interesting points: The sighting was reported by a civilian source
'Saucer' described to move at a very high rate of speed
The conclusion was 'Unidentified' with no definitive explanation
The object made a sudden burst of speed and circled from right to left in a huge circle
